author: AP
title: Browns call latest rumors of trading OBJ "completely false"
description: The Browns say the newest trade rumors about star wide receiver Odell Beckham Jr. are false
content:
CLEVELAND (AP) — Browns chief strategy officer Paul DePodesta dismissed a report the team is trying to trade star wide receiver Odell Beckham Jr., whose future — whether in New York or Cleveland or anywhere — always seems in question.
